      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Interview wording",
      "fontSize": 22,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Interview wording",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 23
    },
    {
      "id": "text-1360122",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 125,
      "y": 4215,
      "width": 1340,
      "height": 50,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#343a40",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "frame-1360004",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1361122,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1362122,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "\u201cThe browser parses the URL, resolves google.com through DNS, opens a TCP connection or QUIC path, performs TLS for HTTPS, sends an HTTP request, receives a response from an edge/load-balanced backend, then parses HTML, loads subresources, runs JavaScript, and renders pixels.\u201d",
      "fontSize": 15,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "\u201cThe browser parses the URL, resolves google.com through DNS, opens a TCP connection or QUIC path, performs TLS for HTTPS, sends an HTTP request, receives a response from an edge/load-balanced backend, then parses HTML, loads subresources, runs JavaScript, and renders pixels.\u201d",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 45
    },
    {
      "id": "text-1360123",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 95,
      "y": 4320,
      "width": 1280,
      "height": 25,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#2b8a3e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "hachure",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": "frame-1360004",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 1361123,
      "version": 1,
      "versionNonce": 1362123,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 0,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Best answer: explain the order, mention caches and security, then connect each step to latency, failure, and scalability.",
      "fontSize": 19,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Best answer: explain the order, mention caches and security, then connect each step to latency, failure, and scalability.",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
      "baseline": 20
    }
  ],
